### Test des Dashboards Personnalisés - Pharma App

### 1. Connexion Autorité de Santé
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "autorite@sante.sn",
    "password": "password"
}

### 2. Dashboard Autorité de Santé (avec token)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/dashboard/autorite
Authorization: Bearer {{token_autorite}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Dashboard Principal Autorité (intelligent)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token_autorite}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Connexion Client
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "client@pharma.sn",
    "password": "password"
}

### 5. Dashboard Client Spécialisé
GET http://localhost:8000/api/dashboard/client
Authorization: Bearer {{token_client}}
Accept: application/json

### 6. Connexion Pharmacien
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login
